Package main.model

Class DonateInfo

java.lang.Object
main.model.DonateInfo
public class DonateInfo extends Object
DonateInfo Class Contains the donate information of Donor. It contains Donor name, Donor phone number, Donated item, Donated item quantity, Remaining donated item quantity and Ngo who received the item.
